{"tid":1190158,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支持　不在於　和平　　支持　在於　反抗暴政","createTime":"2019-06-07T07:25:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T10:07:32.000Z","uid":47714,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"285f4d475e479c555d9158a48b698eb77b572dec","tid":1190158,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T07:25:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10157165135667357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10157165135667357&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8uk4axDeVXns42j9POfnWuxs%3D&h=416092e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10157165135667357</a><br />\n<br />\nSian Lo Lung:<br />\n就像六四，根本不需和平。阿拉伯之春、茉莉花革命、敘利亞的情況，國際一樣支持。國際支持不是在於是否所謂和平，是在於反抗暴政。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10157170719612357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10157170719612357&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8uk4axDeVXns42j9POfnWuxs%3D&h=0fc42507\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10157170719612357</a><br />\n<br />\n因此, 就算你認為他是德國國會案, 你就算有很大證據指出是解放軍放火, 給你在街上抓到有個解放軍穿著軍服跪下來認好不好? 政府還是會做下去的.<br />\n<br />\n就算大家都知道是解放軍做的, 香港會有一堆人反應是問題還是在於你有人反抗, 解放軍就算擺明嫁禍於你, 只要政府控制下局勢穩定下來, 問題就解決. 當你的目標是「不想亂」而不是「維持正義」時, 你會選擇解決弱者, 因為弱者能被解決, 強者不能. 而我們要維持正義, 就不能誣捏任何人, 可是我知道大家都是不想亂, 哪怕包括民主派自己."},{"pid":"cd1652bb56a2f817d58f7979ac664654932016e9","tid":1190158,"uid":59753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T07:27:27.000Z","msg":"岩呀 成班弱智係度執著於鬼唔鬼"},{"pid":"af5eb97e13342bd5eefa927d99f6ab43b83558e8","tid":1190158,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T10:07:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}